EdjePlayer is a application to play standalone Edje files.

This is a perfect example for EdjePlayer:
http://www.gurumeditation.it/blog/enlightenment/calculator/


Allowed data block values
--------------------------
It's possible to set some values in the Edje file data block to control
the behaviour of EdjePlayer. These values are supported until now:

alpha: bool
borderless: bool
shaped: bool
sticky: bool
title: string

Data type reference:
--------------------
bool: "TRUE", "true", "FALSE", "false", "0", "1"
